            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1664883824119-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo </strong>with your<strong> dried oregano</strong>, <strong>dried basil</strong>, <strong>remaining chopped garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!), <strong>remaining white wine vinegar </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/1 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>garlic & herb mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
