            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1664883830280-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy sausage sauce</strong> over the <strong>nachos</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the<strong> garlic & herb mayo </strong>and garnish with the<strong> quick-pickled chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
